inductive with ⟨h_size, h⟩
    apply Array.ext
    · rw [h_size, f_readyForRupAdd.2.1]
    · intro i hi1 hi2
      have i_lt_n : i < n := by rw [← f_readyForRupAdd.2.1]; exact hi2
      specialize h ⟨i, i_lt_n⟩
      rcases h with ⟨h,_⟩
      · exact h
      · omega
theorem clauses_performRupCheck {n : Nat}
